Research Fields

     * Environment
       [a513ec5f92c8a0f68e7ecb30208acaad0942c683_trans_environment-a.png]
       Terrestrial biodiversity and agriculture, marine biodiversity and
       fishing resources, natural disasters, climate change and climate
       migration, pollution, resilient cities...
       Funded projects
     * Health
       [e54b819fef56c43ac736f4c7404464c80d62bb30_trans_health-a.png]
       Demographics, longevity and ageing, well-being, prevention and
       personalized health, management of chronic and non-communicable
       diseases (cancer, cardiovascular diseases, diabetes...), management
       of healthcare systems...
       Funded projects
     * New technologies
       [e143c0fb6a0ad4961bed79f2c1d263660b2742ee_trans_technology-a.png]
       Artificial intelligence, data science and machine learning, cyber
       risk and protection, robotics, autonomous vehicles...
       Funded projects
     * Socio-Economics
       [a3e35cc16ac37992c5a327f01c8c36f74ae30b58_trans_economics-a.png]
       Inclusive finance, behavioral economics, systemic risks, financial
       modelling, geopolitical risks...
       Funded projects

